verbose_text: To assess in depth whether such changes in T cell phenotype and in TF expression could be observed in human-adenovector-vaccine-induced responses, we analyzed further CD8 + T cells primed using a chimpanzee adenovirus strategy (ChAd3), specific for dominant HCV epitopes from NS3 (NS3 95, HLA-A2 restricted and NS3 103 HLA-A1 restricted).
